properties.name: Fires Over Oaklore
properties.description: Sir Baumbard has asked that you ride his dragon into battle and help defend Oaklore Keep from the waves of attacking undead.
properties.complete: You have done it! You have thinned out the waves of attacking undead. The knights of the Pactogonal Table cheer when you and Glumbert land, and award you with a Defender's Medal for defending Oaklore Keep!
